WEBVTT

00:00.501 --> 00:01.499
<i>Previously on "Switched at birth..."</i>

00:04.683 --> 00:07.208
- That's great!
- Are you Ms. Munoz?

00:07.209 --> 00:08.958
I had a baby here 16 years ago.

00:08.959 --> 00:10.671
I remember putting her in her crib,

00:10.672 --> 00:12.369
and I thought it was the right one.

00:12.370 --> 00:13.903
If it was me, I'm sorry.

00:15.897 --> 00:17.134
Hello.

00:17.317 --> 00:18.840
It's really nice to meet you.

00:18.841 --> 00:19.906
I went out on a limb to put you on

00:19.907 --> 00:21.830
this team and I'm starting
to regret that decision.

00:21.831 --> 00:23.232
You put me on the team because I'm deaf

00:23.233 --> 00:25.149
and the school gets disability funding.

00:25.150 --> 00:27.384
Okay, so what did you
really think of Bay's work?

00:27.385 --> 00:29.606
I'm looking for artists that
have something unique to say.

00:29.607 --> 00:30.762
That painting of yours

00:30.763 --> 00:32.593
would go great in a show
I'm putting together.

00:32.594 --> 00:33.904
I think it would really fit in well.

00:33.905 --> 00:35.486
I heard we're going up against each other.

00:35.487 --> 00:37.219
Tell him you don't want
to go out for guard.

00:37.220 --> 00:38.888
I'm not doing that.

00:38.889 --> 00:42.417
Wow. I guess you're not
the friend that I thought you were.

